title: Rise of Nations - Thrones and Patriots Works Online
description:
INSTRUCTIONS
(follow these instructions, not the ones in the txt file inside the torrent)

1.Install Rise of Nations using this key: see .txt file
2.Mount the Thrones & Patriots iso image and install the game using ANY cd key (press random letters and numbers).
3.Enter the game and check for updates to install the latest patch.
4.Replace the exe files from SKIDROW folder with the ones in the Rise of Nations folder.
5.Run the game, create account and play online.
6.Enjoy!

Note! Only tested with this version of the game, but it is possible to work with different ones.
See you all in-game where i'll be playing as civilizatu.


SEED AS LONG AS YOU CAN!
